<template>
    <loading v-model:active="isLoading"
             :can-cancel="false"
             :on-cancel="onCancel"
             :is-full-page="fullPage"/>

        <PageHeader :title="title" :items="items" />
    </Layout>
</template>

import PageHeader from "@/components/page-header";
export default {
    components: {Loading, Layout, PageHeader},
    data(){
        return {
            title: "Fiches contribuables",

        }
    }

}
</script>
